@startuml
actor Customer
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "customer-service" as CustomerService
database "MySQL Customer DB" as CustomerDB

Customer -> Gateway: POST /api/customers/login/
Gateway -> CustomerService: POST /customers/login/
CustomerService -> CustomerDB: Verify username/password
CustomerDB --> CustomerService: Customer account
CustomerService --> Gateway: JWT access/refresh
Gateway --> Customer: Login response
@enduml
